Whitney’s idol, author Robert Greene (THE 48 LAWS OF POWER, THE ART OF SEDUCTION), is back on GOOD FOR YOU and talking to Whitney about everything from the mafia and Elizabeth Holmes to the S&M scene in Germany and farting as the ultimate power move. Robert’s new book THE DAILY LAWS: 366 MEDITATIONS ON POWER is out now.
